<%- include('partials/header') %>

  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Why Use a Travel Advisor?</h1>
    <p>Let me handle the details so you can focus on the adventure</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="reasons">

      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-number">1</div>
        <div class="reason-body">
          <h3>Deep Industry Expertise at Your Fingertips</h3>
          <p>
            I've invested countless hours training with major travel brands&mdash;and plenty of
            boutique ones, too&mdash;so I bring a broad, up-to-date knowledge of what's out there.
            That means I can match you with destinations, resorts, and cruise lines you might never
            have discovered on your own, saving you the endless scrolling and second-guessing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-number">2</div>
        <div class="reason-body">
          <h3>Peace of Mind When Things Don't Go as Planned</h3>
          <p>
            Even the most carefully planned trip can hit a snag&mdash;a delayed flight, a room mix-up,
            an unexpected schedule change. When that happens, you don't have to spend your vacation
            on hold with customer service. Just reach out to me and I'll sort it out while you get
            back to enjoying yourself.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-number">3</div>
        <div class="reason-body">
          <h3>Exclusive Perks You Won't Find Online</h3>
          <p>
            Because I work closely with professionals across the travel industry, I sometimes have
            access to upgrades and extras that aren't available to the general public. Onboard
            credit, early check-in, room upgrades, complimentary amenities&mdash;you never know
            what bonus might get added to your trip.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-number">4</div>
        <div class="reason-body">
          <h3>My Services Are Free to You</h3>
          <p>
            Here's something most people don't realize: a travel advisor's commission is already
            built into the price of every trip, whether you book through an agent or not. The
            travel companies pay me directly from their end. So instead of letting that money stay
            with a big corporation, you get personalized guidance, a dedicated advocate, and the
            satisfaction of supporting a small business&mdash;all at no extra cost.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <h2>Ready to Plan Your Next Getaway?</h2>
      <p>I'd love to hear about your dream trip. Let's make it happen!</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-coral">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
